        </ul>

        <h2>4. Security of Your Information</h2>
        <p>We take appropriate technical and organizational measures to safeguard your personal information against unauthorized access, misuse, and loss. While we strive to protect your information, no system can be 100% secure. You are encouraged to use secure passwords and report any suspicious activity immediately.</p>

